title: GoPro: Five-year-old 'Mini Bruce Lee'
description:
Bruce Lee has inspired many but few as dedicated as five-year-old, Ryusei Imai. Motivated by his idol, Ryusei practices Nanchaku every day.

Special thanks to Naotomo Umewaka.

Shot 100% on the HERO4®

Courtesy of ExtremeMusic

transcripts: [Music Playing] My name is Ryusei Imai. I'm five years old. You have a nickname, right? Mini Lee. Mini Lee? When I grow up? I want to be just like Bruce Lee. I will always use my nun-chucks.
